title: Curiosium Bukit Timah Road
description: Curiosium is a play-and-learn destination where curiosity comes alive. It features 10 interactive stations where kids and adults can paint a life-size dinosaur, build with giant yellow foam blocks, explore the magic of light, experiment with slime, and reimagine LEGO creations. Every visit includes a Curio-Capsule Workshop, a hands-on activity with a take-home item. With workshops changing every week, no two visits are ever the same. Located at Bukit Timah Road, Curiosium is the perfect place for families to learn, play, and make lasting memories together.
datetime_display: Monday - Friday: 5 PM - 8 PM Saturday - Sunday: 9 AM-8 PM

title: Curiosium Science Education Centre Activities
blurb: Engaging science activities for kids and families.
description: Curiosium is a science education centre offering a range of hands-on activities and workshops designed to make learning science fun and engaging for children and families. The centre provides an interactive environment where kids can explore scientific concepts through experiments, demonstrations, and play. It aims to foster curiosity and a love for science in young minds. Activities include science camps, workshops, and open play sessions. The centre is dedicated to providing a fun and educational experience for all visitors, encouraging them to discover the wonders of science in a stimulating and supportive setting.

title: Curiosium Bukit Timah - Creative Play Space
blurb: Explore a world of creativity and imagination.
description: Curiosium Bukit Timah offers a unique creative play space for children. Our space is designed to inspire imagination and foster creativity through a variety of engaging activities. We provide a safe and stimulating environment where children can explore, learn, and grow. Our play areas include interactive exhibits, art stations, and building zones, all designed to encourage hands-on learning and creative expression. We also offer workshops and classes for children of all ages, led by experienced instructors who are passionate about helping children develop their creative potential. Our goal is to provide a space where children can discover their talents, build confidence, and have fun while learning.
